<bibRefCitation author="Frey-Gessner, E" journalOrPublisher="Schaffhausen" pageId="93" pageNumber="94" title="Fauna insectorum helvetiae. Hymenoptera. I. Chrysididae (Die Goldwespen)." year="1887">Frey-Gessner 1887</bibRefCitation>
